    public class Graph
extends org.jfree.chart.ChartPanel
implements SettingOwner, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, java.util.Observer, java.awt.print.Printable
    This class represents multiple series on a single unit graph; all series are rendered together by MultiGraphView.
